: ["なんで", "かなー。"]}, {"box": [145, 1029, 199, 1112], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["？"]}], "img_path": "134.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [360, 1030, 637, 1096], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["タルＤＶＤ"]}], "img_path": "135.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [89, 22, 479, 189], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["プロ・ＤＶＤレンタル"]}, {"box": [719, 314, 734, 340], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["！"]}, {"box": [452, 304, 479, 391], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["高木さん。"]}, {"box": [373, 300, 395, 342], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [694, 829, 746, 918], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あ、西片", "偶然だね。"]}, {"box": [599, 832, 651, 931], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["映画借りに", "来たの？"]}, {"box": [111, 836, 220, 928], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["うん、", "今日", "ヒマだし。"]}], "img_path": "136.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [657, 103, 737, 295], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["最近出た", "荒野のガンマン２」を", "観ようと思ってさ。"]}, {"box": [301, 55, 324, 123], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あはは。"]}, {"box": [91, 99, 144, 195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["好きだねぇ", "西部劇"]}, {"box": [650, 521, 697, 659], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["高木さんは", "何借りに来たの？"]}, {"box": [135, 526, 234, 669], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["私は", "いいのあったら", "借りようかなって", "カンジだよ。"]}, {"box": [705, 823, 755, 892], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ふーん", "そっか。"]}, {"box": [487, 817, 516, 853], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["あ。"]}, {"box": [345, 820, 395, 936], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["レ．．．レンタル", "中．．．"]}, {"box": [127, 850, 149, 919], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ありゃ。"]}, {"box": [494, 980, 520, 1114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["荒野のガシマシ２"]}, {"box": [467, 978, 487, 1115], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["荒野のガンマン２"]}, {"box": [433, 978, 456, 1115], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["荒野のガシマン２"]}], "img_path": "137.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [728, 71, 780, 154], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["残念", "だったね。"]}, {"box": [572, 78, 619, 166], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["観たかった", "のになぁ．．．"]}, {"box": [424, 63, 490, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "何か他のやつ", "借りようかな。"]}, {"box": [274, 117, 304, 155], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["あ。"]}, {"box": [99, 193, 120, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["じゃあさ、"]}, {"box": [649, 498, 728, 603], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["お互い", "おすすめ", "１本選んで、"]}, {"box": [154, 521, 212, 613], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["交換", "しようよ。"]}, {"box": [708, 899, 750, 983], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["なるほど。"]}, {"box": [442, 921, 463, 985], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いいね。"]}, {"box": [326, 907, 402, 1023], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["うん、", "じゃあ探して", "くるねー。"]}], "img_path": "138.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [432, 116, 451, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ふふふ．．．"]}, {"box": [650, 532, 729, 704], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["めっちゃ", "こわいのを", "おすすめしてやる。"]}, {"box": [556, 850, 602, 881], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [447, 861, 497, 930], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["これも", "いいな。"]}, {"box": [697, 860, 746, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どれが", "いいかなー。"]}, {"box": [402, 979, 452, 1087], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["うん、", "これもいい。"]}], "img_path": "139.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [673, 938, 693, 1004], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [269, 925, 349, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["普通に", "おすすめを", "探すか．．．"]}], "img_path": "140.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [485, 98, 537, 202], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["決まった", "みたいだね。"]}, {"box": [353, 148, 380, 203], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["うん。"]}, {"box": [698, 643, 747, 796], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["オレのおすすめは", "これ！"]}, {"box": [291, 652, 366, 778], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あはは、", "やっぱり", "西部劇なんだ。"]}, {"box": [96, 651, 170, 777], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いやいや、", "ちょっと", "違うんだって。"]}, {"box": [326, 952, 376, 1086], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ふーん", "どんな話なの？"]}], "img_path": "141.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [632, 123, 756, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["西部劇かと", "思いきや、", "実は未来の", "話でね。"]}, {"box": [461, 116, 540, 278], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["地球はうちうじん", "宇宙人と戦争に", "なりそうなんだよ。"]}, {"box": [332, 107, 405, 262], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["てもムダな血を", "流すのを", "好まない宇宙人が"]}, {"box": [200, 107, 299, 243], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["地球式の代表者", "一名ずつの", "決闘をしようと", "言ってきて、"]}, {"box": [702, 505, 749, 627], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["へえー", "面白そうだね。"]}, {"box": [511, 276, 587, 348], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["それはそうですか．．．"]}, {"box": [422, 543, 444, 622], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["でしょ！"]}, {"box": [274, 494, 350, 619], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そして", "ラストの", "どんでん返し。"]}, {"box": [96, 276, 169, 400], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["それに", "主人公が", "選ばれるんだ。"]}, {"box": [615, 871, 728, 987], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["なんと", "主人公も", "宇宙人", "だったんだ。"]}], "img_path": "142.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [733, 87, 754, 148], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あれ？"]}, {"box": [475, 69, 507, 101], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["今、"]}, {"box": [428, 125, 452, 263], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ネタバレした？"]}, {"box": [363, 103, 386, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["え？"]}, {"box": [259, 117, 278, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [186, 101, 215, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あぁああ。"]}, {"box": [423, 550, 506, 629], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あ", "あ"]}, {"box": [685, 585, 736, 680], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ゴ．．．ゴメン", "つい．．．"]}, {"box": [537, 581, 641, 662], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["すぐ", "別のやつ", "探して", "くるよ．．．"]}, {"box": [134, 583, 186, 651], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["んーん、", "いいよ。"]}, {"box": [730, 923, 749, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["これにする。"]}, {"box": [332, 933, 386, 999], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "でも．．．"]}], "img_path": "143.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [706, 75, 785, 209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["せっかく西片が", "選んでくれた", "映画だしね。"]}, {"box": [331, 113, 350, 178], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [105, 165, 127, 244], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["そっか．．．"]}, {"box": [690, 537, 742, 637], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["じゃあ次は", "私ね。"]}, {"box": [632, 536, 659, 588], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["これ。"]}, {"box": [678, 848, 696, 923], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["なんと"]}, {"box": [160, 547, 195, 691], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["「私の新しい朝」。"]}, {"box": [93, 871, 126, 925], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["へー。"]}, {"box": [723, 853, 753, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["感動もの？"]}, {"box": [440, 856, 489, 982], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["まぁ", "そうだけどね。"]}, {"box": [274, 843, 401, 1025], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["でもバトルもあるし、", "西片も", "楽しめる", "かなーって。"]}], "img_path": "144.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [728, 110, 753, 244], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["どんな話なの？"]}, {"box": [407, 117, 507, 287], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["おたずね者の", "主人公が", "いろんな賞金稼ぎと", "戦いながら、"]}, {"box": [255, 113, 359, 268], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["病気で死にそうな", "昔の友達に", "会いに行く", "話だよ。"]}, {"box": [82, 52, 371, 72], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [103, 192, 154, 289], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["おお、", "面白そう！！"]}, {"box": [638, 514, 692, 630], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["決闘シーンも", "あるよ。"]}, {"box": [172, 498, 193, 576], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["すごい！！"]}, {"box": [96, 523, 142, 676], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["オレめちゃくちゃ", "楽しめそうだよ。"]}, {"box": [468, 861, 542, 959], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["しかし．．．", "そうなると", "余計に、"]}, {"box": [124, 858, 175, 975], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ネタバレして", "ゴメン．．．"]}], "img_path": "145.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [638, 52, 739, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あはは、", "ホントに", "気にしなくて", "いいのに。"]}, {"box": [533, 48, 552, 113], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [247, 89, 301, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["あのさ", "西片。"]}, {"box": [651, 489, 702, 605], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "おわびにさ．．．"]}, {"box": [466, 837, 483, 903], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [392, 1040, 420, 1136], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["高木さん？"]}], "img_path": "146.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [591, 125, 698, 243], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["お互い", "もう一本ずつ", "おすすめ", "選ばうよ。"]}, {"box": [171, 108, 217, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ヒマって", "言ってたし、"]}, {"box": [94, 159, 141, 285], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["２本くらい", "観れるでしょ。"]}, {"box": [97, 401, 149, 455], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["あ．．．", "うん。"]}, {"box": [694, 786, 745, 864], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["じゃあね", "西片。"]}, {"box": [388, 797, 410, 846], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["うん。"]}, {"box": [99, 810, 151, 874], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "また。"]}], "img_path": "147.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [630, 701, 678, 823], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いっつも", "大切なとこで、"]}, {"box": [193, 703, 276, 803], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["勇気", "出ないなー", "私は。"]}], "img_path": "148.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [673, 526, 694, 586], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["い．．．？"]}, {"box": [164, 519, 217, 639], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["えいという事がしい", "映画だった．．．"]}, {"box": [726, 828, 747, 886], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["はー．．．"]}, {"box": [107, 598, 131, 740], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["「私の新しい朝。"]}, {"box": [376, 843, 509, 960], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["また映画", "借りるときは", "高木さんに", "おすすめを", "聞こう．．"]}, {"box": [258, 834, 332, 978], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そうだ、", "もう一本", "あるんだったな。"]}, {"box": [92, 956, 113, 1022], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["えーと。"]}], "img_path": "149.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [178, 73, 199, 170], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["これって．．．"]}, {"box": [474, 63, 494, 128], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [146, 479, 188, 515], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [335, 992, 486, 1054], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["っしょにみようよ"]}, {"box": [240, 1150, 602, 1175], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["一からかい上手の高木さん四・完一"]}, {"box": [597, 915, 697, 1032], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["いやいや、", "そんなワケ", "ない．．．", "考えすぎだ．．．"]}], "img_path": "150.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "151.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [610, 186, 691, 316], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そういえば", "わざわざ階段", "数えたの？"]}, {"box": [325, 72, 506, 121], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おまけ"]}, {"box": [162, 225, 220, 314], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["いやー、", "それが．．．"]}, {"box": [242, 735, 295, 793], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ん？", "西片。"]}], "img_path": "152.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [707, 101, 735, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ、中井君。"]}, {"box": [547, 111, 572, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["よー。"]}, {"box": [483, 108, 507, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["何してんの？"]}, {"box": [155, 125, 183, 165], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あー"]}, {"box": [99, 151, 124, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["いやー．．．"]}, {"box": [672, 499, 746, 645], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["．．．うまい", "空気が", "吸いたくてさー。"]}, {"box": [346, 489, 374, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["西片は？"]}, {"box": [100, 495, 179, 619], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あーここの", "階段が何段か", "数えてて．．．"]}, {"box": [641, 791, 723, 942], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ああ．．．！", "今何段か", "忘れちゃった！！"]}, {"box": [148, 827, 183, 916], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["４１５段だ。"]}], "img_path": "153.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [684, 170, 704, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["へ？"]}, {"box": [425, 123, 478, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["全部で", "４１５段だよ。"]}, {"box": [330, 96, 378, 208], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["なんで", "知ってるの？"]}, {"box": [97, 146, 123, 215], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あー．．．"]}, {"box": [597, 487, 700, 586], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["オレも", "なんとなく", "数えて", "たんだよ。"]}, {"box": [216, 483, 269, 564], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["へー", "そっか！！"]}, {"box": [133, 502, 179, 615], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["助かったよ", "ありがとう！"]}, {"box": [600, 680, 647, 783], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ってことが", "あってさー。"]}, {"box": [221, 802, 247, 876], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ふーん。"]}], "img_path": "154.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [698, 138, 722, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いいな、"]}, {"box": [326, 146, 356, 258], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["真野ちゃん。"]}, {"box": [82, 52, 372, 72], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかいと手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [208, 116, 235, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [433, 672, 481, 751], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どういう", "こと？"]}, {"box": [616, 901, 667, 969], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["おしえ", "なーい。"]}, {"box": [193, 892, 227, 943], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["え！？"]}, {"box": [139, 942, 160, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["なんで！？"]}, {"box": [46, 1014, 72, 1102], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["おわり"]}], "img_path": "155.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [131, 93, 609, 142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [133, 180, 568, 203], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ゲッサン少年サンデー・コミックススペシャル"]}, {"box": [195, 547, 500, 563], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["２０２０年８月１７日初版第１刷発行"]}, {"box": [439, 513, 759, 528], "vertical": false, "font_size": 13.5, "lines": ["０９－８５０２１０－３", "ＩＳＢＮ９７８－４－Ｃ"]}, {"box": [193, 651, 262, 685], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["著", "者"]}, {"box": [197, 726, 262, 787], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["発行者", "ＥＤＦＵＰＥ"]}, {"box": [137, 825, 603, 931], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.75, "lines": ["「ゲッサン」２０１９年８月号、１月号、２０１７年号〜６月号掲載作品", "連載担当／板谷真人", "単行本編集責任ノ石川昌彦", "単行本編集ノ板谷真人。〈三輪狼子（アイブロダクション）"]}, {"box": [402, 651, 664, 751], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.333333333333332, "lines": ["山本宗一朗", "ＣＳＳｉｃｈｉｒｏｙａｎａｍａｎｏｎｏ．２０１", "樹正田細"]}, {"box": [407, 767, 616, 783], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["中央精版印刷株式会社"]}, {"box": [142, 942, 240, 979], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["発行所"]}, {"box": [256, 943, 599, 962], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["〈〒１０－８００】東京都千代田区一ツ橋二の三の"]}, {"box": [138, 1027, 762, 1142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["●法本には十分注意しでおりますが、印刷、製本なと製造上の不備がございましたら「制作局コール", "センター「パフリーダイヤルＩＤＡ」３８６－６８２にご連絡ください。", "〈電話受付は、土・日・提供日を除く９，３０〜１７：８０", "●本書の一部または全部を無断で複製、転載、複写（コピー）、スキャン、デジタル化、上演、放送", "等をすることは、著作権法上での例外を除き禁じられています。代行業者等の第三者による本書の", "電子的複製も認められておりません。"]}, {"box": [425, 965, 741, 1018], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["２０１８年１１月１２日に編集のパスターマッチング", "平成２８年１０月２８日、現在は５８０１５年６月１５日（月）第３６日（日）第１５回"]}], "img_path": "156.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [103, 761, 716, 945], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さん１４", "山本崇一朗", "○山本崇一朗ノ小学館", "書名著者名", "株式会社小学年", "行", "発", "〒１０１－８００１．東京都千代田区一ツ橋２・３－"]}, {"box": [121, 992, 574, 1021], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["電子書籍制作会社株式会社社昭和ブライト"]}, {"box": [123, 1065, 661, 1106], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["氷収録されている作品は、執筆された当時の状況や年代を考慮の上、", "初回掲載時の表現のまま掲載されております。ご了承ください。"]}], "img_path": "157.jpg"}]}